    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Leptotrombidium gracipalpe (Schluger, 1960), lectotype. A, dorsal aspect of idiosoma; B, scutum. Scale bars: 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5591532/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5593322>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Leptotrombidium gracipalpe (Schluger, 1960). A, scutum of lectotype; B, humeral seta (C antero-marginal) of lectotype; C, dorsal idiosomal seta of lectotype; D, postanal seta of lectotype; E, preanal seta of lectotype; F, arrangement of dorsal idiosomal setae of lectotype; G, ventral aspect of idiosoma of lectotype; H, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3272, specimen 2; I, ventral aspect of gnathosoma in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3272, specimen 2; J, leg I (trochanter–tarsus) in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3266, specimen 6; K, leg II (trochanter–tarsus) in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt- 3266, specimen 6; L, leg III (trochanter–tarsus) in paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3266, specimen 6.Abbreviations as in Fig. 2. Scale bars: 50 μm (A–E), 100 μm (F, G), 50 μm (H, I), 50 μm (J–L)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5593322/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

